/p>\n\n<h2>非递归实现</h2>\n\n<p>我们继续查看刚刚的规律</p>\n\n<pre>\n<code>当 n = 2的时候， h = f(1) + f(0) = 1 + 0 = 1\n当 n = 3的时候， h = f(2) + f(1) = 1 + 1 = 2\n当 n = 4的时候， h = f(3) + f(2) = 3 + 1 = 4\n</code></pre>\n\n<p>我们可以从n = 2，一直循环，直到我们计算出我们输入的值为n的时候</p>\n\n<p>我们只需要从最小的开始计算，每次保留中间结果，最后得出我们的第n个的结果。</p>\n\n<pre>\n<code># 大家都知道斐波那契数列，现在要求输入一个整数n，请你输出斐波那契数列的第n项（从0开始，第0项为0）  n&lt;=39\nclass Solution:\n\n    # 非递归实现\n    # 当 n = 2的时候， h = f(1) + f(0) = 1 + 0 = 1\n    # 当 n = 3的时候， h = f(2) + f(1) = 1 + 1 = 2\n    # 当 n = 4的时候， h = f(3) + f(2) = 3 + 1 = 4\n    def Fibonacci2(self, n):\n        if n == 0:\n            return 0;\n        if n == 1:\n            return 1;\n\n        ret = 0\n        a = 1\n        b = 0\n        for i in range(0, n-1):\n            ret = a + b\n            b = a\n            a = ret\n        return ret\n\nif __name__ == \'__main__\':\n    print(Solution().Fibonacci2(10))\n</code></pre>\n, tagUid=5c4c541e600ff422ccb371ee788f59d6, blogSortUid=718c76d4a84e408da23e04949a75e7e8, fileUid=d134bdfe255b9aa8c2ce44da8297f6a6, adminUid=1f01cd1d2f474743b241d74008b12333, isPublish=1, isOriginal=1, author=陌溪, articlesPart=蘑菇博客, level=0, tagList=[Tag(content=测试标签, clickCount=2, sort=12)], photoList=[http://localhost:8600//blog/admin/jpg/2020/2/1/1580528781247.jpg], blogSort=BlogSort(sortName=测试3, content=测试3, clickCount=0, sort=1), praiseCount=null, copyright=null, levelKeyword=null, useSort=0, sort=0, startComment=1)]}','删除选中博客',1,'2020-04-28 09:18:14','2020-04-28 09:18:14','XX|XX|内网IP|内网IP',230),('f35144b26a06e2031eff1a30b51cb7d0','admin','1f01cd1d2f474743b241d74008b12333','192.168.80.1','/picture/setCover','POST','com.moxi.mogublog.admin.restapi.PictureRestApi','setCover','{\"result\":org.springframework.validation.BeanPropertyBindingResult: 0 errors,\"pictureVO\":PictureVO(fileUid=null, fileUids=null, picName=null, pictureSortUid=976dbeb57cb6d5234c1c73e1de8522cf)}','通过图片Uid将图片设为封面',1,'2020-04-07 15:45:58','2020-04-07 15:45:58','XX|XX|内网IP|内网IP',144),('f37fd41a9b46dfd